Slipping back into routine, gently and gratefully. 💛🌻📸

The past few weeks have been heavy both personally and for our nation. Posting and pretending everything was well just didn’t feel right in the midst of it all.

Hoping for safety, peace, and healing for everyone, especially our Indian ARMY eternally grateful for everything they’ve done and continue to do for India. Jai Hind 🤍🫂🇮🇳

And as things slowly settle, I’m finding my way back to something that brings me joy, CREATING 📸🎞️

Here’s to softer days and consistent little joys again💗🌸

latestPosts.caption:
Latte and Explore: Episode 1 – @ate_altogetherexperimental, Safdarjung ☕✨

A cafe that feels like a warm hug? Say less. “Ate” is small but beautifully carved into cozy “caves” that make you feel like you have your own little world—privacy, but make it aesthetic.

I had to try their coffee, and let’s just say… my caffeine cravings were more than satisfied. The flavor? Chef’s kiss. Would I go back just for it? Absolutely.

But the real showstopper? Their desserts. Genuinely some of the most stunningly crafted treats I’ve seen. I tried the blueberry & lavender gateaux—a unique flavor mix that left me with mixed feelings, but hey, that just means I need to come back and try more.

Can’t wait to revisit and have a long, much-needed yapping session with my friends. Have you been here yet? Let me know your go-to cafe in the comments! ☕✨ #LatterAndExplore
